_sText:
From the [original map](http://maps.cs-bg.info/maps/cs/119/) made for Counter-Strike, arrives 35hp_2Source, the classic map now available for Counter-Strike: Source.

This map uses the same design as the original one, but with some different textures as they can no longer be found or don't fit the map's style, along with a new Skybox texture (from cs_italy).

I hope you'll enjoy this map as I do in Counter-Strike.
